243
00:19:44,504 --> 00:19:45,923
Freaks.

244
00:19:46,844 --> 00:19:48,417
Yeah.

245
00:19:57,702 --> 00:19:59,236
Hey.

246
00:20:14,430 --> 00:20:15,888
What the hell, man?

247
00:20:16,079 --> 00:20:18,765
