Stocks.

761
01:19:45,687 --> 01:19:49,140
WilPharma stock tanked
because of our accusations.

762
01:19:49,332 --> 01:19:51,365
You were afraid that the situation...

763
01:19:51,596 --> 01:19:54,281
...would turn out the same
as it did for Umbrella Corporation.

764
01:19:54,512 --> 01:19:56,929
So you needed an excuse
to use the vaccine.

765
01:19:57,120 --> 01:19:58,924
Now, wait a minute.

766
01:19:59,116 --> 01:20:00,957
Yes, I'm a stockholder.

767
01:20:01,149 --> 01:20:04,986
And WilPharma should regain
the public's faith after this incident.

768
01:20:05,178 --> 01:20:09,321
But there's no way in hell I would
support terrorism to ensure that.

769
01:20:09,513 --> 01:20:12,889
First of all, what is the G-virus?
I've never even heard of it.

770
01:20:13,081 --> 01:20:16,419
I know you ordered Frederic
to dispose of the G-virus...

771
01:20:16,611 --> 01:20:17,685
...when you called him.

772
01:20:17,877 --> 01:20:19,949
I told him
not to show you anything more...

773
01:20:20,179 --> 01:20:22,481
...than you needed to see,
that was it.

774
01:20:22,673 --> 01:20:24,361
I doubt he knows anything.

775
01:20:24,783 --> 01:20:25,857
Leon.

776
01:20:26,049 --> 01:20:28,006
General Grande's
communication man talked.

777
01:20:28,236 --> 01:20:32,495
It seems that all of us, the senator
included, were fooled by him.

778
01:20:32,687 --> 01:20:35,372
Who are you talking about?

779
01:20:43,698 --> 01:20:46,460
- Frederic? Where are you?
- In Level 4.

780
01:20:46,652 --> 01:20:48,724
Why? You said you were
going to the server room.

781
01:20:48,916 --> 01:20:51,448
I saw someone suspicious
on my way there and followed him.

782
01:20:51,640 --> 01:20:52,599
You need to get out.

783
01:20:52,791 --> 01:20:55,054
There's a time bomb here.
It's too late to stop it.

784
01:21:00,426 --> 01:21:03,457
We'll have another biohazard
if this thing-

785
01:21:06,871 --> 01:21:08,943
It can't be.

786
01:21:11,283 --> 01:21:12,473
It's me.

787
01:21:12,933 --> 01:21:14,852
What do you think?

788
01:21:15,043 --> 01:21:18,420
Yes, per your request.

789
01:21:20,108 --> 01:21:21,911
As of now, General Grande...

790
01:21:22,103 --> 01:21:23,676
...only you will be in possession...

791
01:21:23,868 --> 01:21:27,167
...of a set
of the T-virus and the T-vaccine.

792
01:21:27,359 --> 01:21:30,352
Nothing would offer greater
advantage when negotiating...

793
01:21:30,582 --> 01:21:34,994
...with a country that wants to keep
the existence of this virus a secret.

794
01:21:42,437 --> 01:21:44,317
You needn't worry.

795
01:21:44,509 --> 01:21:46,965
I've anticipated everything
down to the last detail...

796
01:21:47,195 --> 01:21:50,341
...including my own
escape arrangements.

797
01:21:51,952 --> 01:21:53,257
Don't forget...

798
01:21:53,449 --> 01:21:57,324
...you owe me extra money
for the data on the G-virus.

799
01:21:58,206 --> 01:21:59,894
And one last thing:

800
01:22:00,086 --> 01:22:01,544
As a friend...

801
01:22:01,736 --> 01:22:05,112
...heed my advice
and forget about G.

802
01:22:05,342 --> 01:22:09,332
The stuff is wickedly volatile,
and it can't be controlled.

803
01:22:15,932 --> 01:22:18,579
Right on time.

804
01:22:28,286 --> 01:22:30,051
You were supposed to come alone.

805
01:22:30,242 --> 01:22:33,158
I just wanted to see your face
one more time.

806
01:22:36,650 --> 01:22:38,338
Don't move.

807
01:22:38,530 --> 01:22:41,062
I have the last of the vaccine,
and the development data.

808
01:22:41,254 --> 01:22:43,671
This is all that remains
in the entire world.

809
01:22:43,863 --> 01:22:45,589
The rest is gone.

810
01:22:48,735 --> 01:22:51,037
Yes, that's right.

811
01:22:51,229 --> 01:22:54,106
You two can appreciate the situation
better than anyone...

812
01:22:54,298 --> 01:22:59,478
...after your up-close-and-personal
experiences with virus victims.

813
01:22:59,785 --> 01:23:02,931
Mankind will need this.

814
01:23:12,407 --> 01:23:15,016
Wait. Please. Don't shoot me.
Let's talk.

815
01:23:15,592 --> 01:23:18,086
You're a smart woman,
and smart women like money.

816
01:23:18,278 --> 01:23:21,654
I can make you rich.
We'll split everything 50-50.

817
01:23:21,846 --> 01:23:24,915
I meant 70-30. I'm happy with 30.

818
01:23:25,107 --> 01:23:27,102
Please. Please, take it all.

819
01:23:27,332 --> 01:23:31,936
Don't- Don't kill me.
I'm begging you. Please, no.

820
01:23:34,123 --> 01:23:37,730
You're too pathetic to kill.

821
01:23:46,784 --> 01:23:48,472
- All units, move in.
- Yes, sir.

822
01:23:48,664 --> 01:23:50,774
Suspect has been apprehended
and is in custody.

823
01:24:33,131 --> 01:24:35,625
Frederic confessed everything.

824
01:24:38,234 --> 01:24:42,262
He was also the one that provided
the T-virus to the terrorists in India.

825
01:24:42,454 --> 01:24:45,677
He even acted
as the black-market broker.

826
01:24:48,286 --> 01:24:49,974
He stole the T- and G-viruses...

827
01:24:50,166 --> 01:24:53,005
...then escaped right before
the Raccoon City disaster.

828
01:24:53,197 --> 01:24:57,379
But Frederic decided he could
only sell them as a set with a vaccine.

829
01:24:57,571 --> 01:24:59,566
So he erased his past...

830
01:24:59,758 --> 01:25:01,369
...found employment
at WilPharma...

831
01:25:01,561 --> 01:25:05,666
...and gained unrestricted access
to their research facilities.

832
01:25:06,012 --> 01:25:08,659
He had the luxury of searching
for potential customers...

833
01:25:08,889 --> 01:25:11,268
...while manufacturing the vaccine.

834
01:25:11,958 --> 01:25:14,529
This is how he stumbled upon
General Grande.

835
01:25:14,721 --> 01:25:16,716
The terrorist incidents
were demonstrations...

836
01:25:16,946 --> 01:25:19,133
...staged for
General Grande's benefit.

837
01:25:19,325 --> 01:25:20,437
Sort of a...

838
01:25:20,629 --> 01:25:23,200
...twisted sales pitch.

839
01:25:25,080 --> 01:25:28,149
And my brother
was just a tool to them.

840
01:25:29,684 --> 01:25:31,794
He was used.

841
01:25:32,369 --> 01:25:35,784
This doesn't absolve Curtis
of what he did.

842
01:25:35,976 --> 01:25:38,393
But we share
something in common with him...

843
01:25:38,585 --> 01:25:40,311
...and that's his passionate desire...

844
01:25:40,503 --> 01:25:43,956
...to prevent any further tragedies
like Raccoon City.

845
01:26:12,309 --> 01:26:14,228
I gotta go.

846
01:26:14,803 --> 01:26:16,491
All right.

847
01:26:17,681 --> 01:26:19,484
Catch you later.

848
01:26:25,277 --> 01:26:27,081
Leon.

849
01:26:30,610 --> 01:26:34,140
Let's go diving together again...

850
01:26:34,332 --> 01:26:35,675
...sometime.

851
01:26:36,480 --> 01:26:38,130
Love to.

852
01:26:50,254 --> 01:26:52,710
When did you two go diving?

853
01:26:53,208 --> 01:26:54,359
Don't worry about that.

854
01:26:54,551 --> 01:26:57,198
More importantly,
what are you up to?

855
01:26:57,390 --> 01:26:59,309
Need a lift?

856
01:26:59,923 --> 01:27:02,570
I have a limousine waiting.

857
01:27:02,762 --> 01:27:04,066
Claire.

858
01:27:07,864 --> 01:27:09,936
Next time
we bump into each other...

859
01:27:10,128 --> 01:27:11,855
...let's hope it's some place...

860
01:27:12,046 --> 01:27:14,770
...a little more normal.

861
01:27:16,459 --> 01:27:18,262
Definitely.

862
01:27:19,336 --> 01:27:21,370
Until next time.

863
01:27:54,634 --> 01:27:57,473
Senator Ron Davis
announced his resignation...

864
01:27:57,703 --> 01:28:00,926
...after being accused of insider
trading with WilPharma stock...

865
01:28:01,118 --> 01:28:04,494
...a company of which
he is a major stockholder.

866
01:28:08,100 --> 01:28:09,980
Next, in international news:

867
01:28:10,172 --> 01:28:13,433
General Miguel Grande
has suddenly decided to participate...

868
01:28:13,625 --> 01:28:15,659
...in a Central Asian
disarmament conference.

869
01:28:15,889 --> 01:28:19,687
But the real motivation behind
his participation is not yet known.

870
01:28:19,917 --> 01:28:23,409
Government sources seem to be
optimistic about the turnaround...

871
01:28:23,600 --> 01:28:26,516
...and say that it is to alleviate
economic blockades...

872
01:28:26,708 --> 01:28:28,588
...while rumors state
that it is because...

873
01:28:28,780 --> 01:28:32,348
...his ability to produce biological
weapons has been removed.



